Package: virtualbmc
Architecture: all
Section: utils
Depends: python3, python3-libvirt, python3-pyghmi, python3-cliff
Description: Simulates a Baseboard Management Controller (BMC)
 by exposing IPMI responder to the network and talking to libvirt at
 the host vBMC is running at to manipulate virtual machines which pretend
 to be bare metal servers.
